av capital—news —news join our mailing list menu about team strategy philosophy portfolio news contact brochure home  news news av capital announces its formation partners with arizonabased kovach building enclosures former leaders of the austin ventures middle market investment practice launch new private equity firm in conjunction with first investment austin texas—january  —av capital an austin texasbased private equity firm that partners with entrepreneurial middle market companies as the firsttime institutional investor formally launched today and simultaneously announced its investment in and partnership with kovach building enclosures participating in the equity of the kovach investment with av capital was orix mezzanine  private equity founded by the former leaders of the middle market investment practice at austin ventures av capital is owned and managed by vernon bryant dave alter and scott donaldson the av capital team has worked together for more than  years while at austin ventures and tgf management has deployed in excess of  million of equity capital in  platform companies and is supported by an experienced group of investors that includes austin ventures founders joe aragona and ken deangelis and tgf management founder jim kozlowski “we are excited to formally announce the launch of av capital which targets the unique needs of closelyheld businesses that are operated by talented management teams with a clear vision for growth” said vernon bryant managing partner at av capital “as a company’s firsttime institutional investor we understand how to partner with our management teams to help realize the full potential of their companies we look forward to applying our proven and consistent approach to investing in middle market companies not only in texas but across the broader united states” av capital seeks to invest  million to  million of equity capital in companies with  million to  million in revenue and  million to  million of ebitda the av capital team has significant experience across a broad range of industries including construction and infrastructure services industrial and energy services business and healthcare services and light manufacturing and distribution the firm excels in ‘rightfit partner’ situations that align with its extensive experience partnering with management teams in closelyheld companies to transition to institutional ownership and accelerate growth both organically and through acquisition kovach building enclosures based in chandler arizona kovach is one the nation’s largest integrated designers manufacturers and installers of high quality panel and glazing systems for commercial building enclosures as a leading provider of customized building enclosure solutions kovach offers a complete line of services to meet the most demanding design applications for unique and complex building projects in the higher education healthcare municipal commercial sports arena and airport end markets “we are thrilled to invest in kovach and complete this significant transaction on an accelerated timeline while simultaneously launching av capital” said dave alter partner at av capital “kovach is an impressive company that fits squarely within av capital’s strategy of partnering with talented management teams to transition wellrun middle market companies to institutional ownership and drive growth we are proud to partner with ceo scott bourdo and president stephen kovach v at an important inflection point in the company’s history and to provide strategic and financial resources in support of management’s long term vision for redefining the building enclosure market on a national scale” kovach chief executive officer scott bourdo commented “we were impressed with the av capital team kovach has a relationshiporiented culture a passion for innovation and a focus on providing quality products and services to our clients av capital’s team has a likeminded approach to partnership a genuine respect and appreciation for our culture and an impressive track record of success in supporting entrepreneurs to build categorydefining companies” kovach president stephen kovach v added “we are in our th year of business and feel like it’s just the beginning of our growth story av capital understands the collaborative nature of our business and has embraced our vision to make kovach a total solutions provider in the commercial building envelope space we’re proud to partner with a firm that has a focus on taking businesses like ours to the next level” about av capital av capital is an austinbased private equity firm that makes control investments in entrepreneurial middle market companies as the firsttime institutional investor av capital is focused exclusively on partnering with talented management teams to transition closelyheld middle market companies to institutional ownership and accelerate growth as relationshiporiented investors av capital brings a patient approach and a long term investment perspective to building market leading companies business owners have chosen to partner with av capital because of its strong values and culture its extensive investment experience and network of relationships and its history of success in supporting the vision of entrepreneurial management teams for further information about av capital please visit wwwavcapital about orix mezzanine  private equity orix mezzanine  private equity offers a variety of junior debt and equity financing options for lower mid to middlemarket companies throughout north america typical investments range from  million to  million with the capacity to grow investments are in a wide variety of industries and transaction types including buyouts and acquisitions growth financings recapitalizations and special situations investing the firm’s own proprietary capital has allowed for a flexible and long term approach to investments that are often not afforded by traditional investment firms orix mezzanine  private equity is a business unit of orix usa wwworixcom a dallasbased financial services firm known for providing innovative capital solutions that clients need to propel their business to the next level with more than  employees spanning  offices across the us and brazil orix usa and its family of companies hold  billion of assets and manage an additional  billion approximately its parent company orix corporation is a tokyobased publicly owned international financial services company with operations in  countries and regions worldwide orix corporation is listed on the tokyo  and new york stock exchanges ix for more information on orix mezzanine  private equity visit wwworixmpecom media inquiries vernon bryant  vernonavcapital   av capital holdings llc all rights reserved bizapediacom  human validation companiespeopleproductsservicestrademarksaddressesphone book our system has detected a high number of page requests from your ip address please prove to us that you are a human to continue using our website please send me to the search subscription offer page after i successfully answer the word challenge bizapediapro searchperform unlimited searches via ouradvanced search form withbizapedia pro searchfind out more bizapediapro databuild custom data listsfor one or many stateswith bizapedia pro datafind out more  copyright   · bizapediacom · all rights reservedblogpro searchpro apicontact usterms of useprivacy policysitemapdesktop version   capital partners  private equity investments capital partners is a differentiated private equity investor focused on building and growing private companies with business owners low leverage approach capitalize our businesses with  equity single debt class with long amortization flexible covenants and low interest rates moderates lender covenant pressure provides management with the flexibility to pursue acquisitions and fund capital expansion higherequity longer term investment horizon partner with business owners and management teams for longer term value creation target investment period of five to ten years current income in addition to longerterm equity gains provides business owners and management teams a quarterly cash distribution on their investment in addition to opportunity to participate in future equity gains current cash yield supports longerterm investment approach partnership and incentive alignment we invest on the same terms as business owners and managers augment direct management ownership with equity incentives to provide opportunity to participate further in current income and capital appreciation to more deeply align interests low leverageapproach longterminvestment horizon currentincome focus partnership andincentive alignment         capital product partners lp k sep    seeking alphasign in  join nowgo»capital product partners lp cplpform k  report of foreign issuersep  about capital product partners lp cplpview as pdf capital product partners lp form k received         united states securities and exchange commission washington dc form k report of foreign private issuer pursuant to rule a or d under the securities exchange act of  date of report september   commission file number  capital product partners lp translation of registrants name into english  iassonos street piraeus  greece address of principal executive offices indicate by check mark whether the registrant files or will file annual reports under cover of form f or form f   form f  þ    form f  ¨ indicate by check mark if the registrant is submitting the form k in paper as permitted by regulation st rule b  ¨ indicate by check mark if the registrant is submitting the form k in paper as permitted by regulation st rule b  ¨ indicate by check mark whether the registrant by furnishing the information contained in this form is also thereby furnishing the information to the commission pursuant to rule gb under the securities exchange act of   yes  ¨       no  þ if yes is marked indicate below the file number assigned to the reg